ple or systems having diverse interests when society fails to create a public that would govern for the common interest.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 4aGesellschaftlicher Zusammenhalt. 4aMoral Codes. 4aMorality. 4aMoralität. 4aMoralkodex. 4aSocial Cohesion. 4aZones. 70(DE-601)1042214960(DE-588)4065654-8aWert2gnd 70(DE-601)1061299290(DE-588)4062868-1aVerhaltensregel2gnd 70(DE-601)10614586X0(DE-588)4058812-9aSystemtheorie2gnd 70(DE-601)1063195900(DE-588)4020015-2aGemeinschaft2gnd 70(DE-601)1063359870(DE-588)4015602-3aEthik2gnd 7aPHILOSOPHY / Ethics & Moral Philosophy.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014 PART1z978311023857008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Backlist Philosophy English Language 2000-2014z978311023848808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2014z9783110370393oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz97831103768450 cprintz978311035192740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110352610423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110352610.jpg  a978-3-11-023848-8  DGBA Backlist Philosophy English Language 2000-2014c2000d2014  aDGBA Backlist Complete English Language 2000-2014c2000d2014  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aPDA7ENG  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DPHb2014  aZDB-23-GPHc